          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉，张广才。曾受赵五娘之托，请我看守坟茔，不免前去洁扫一番。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦呵呵……看空山寂寂，悲风萧瑟，好凄凉人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清江引导板） 黄叶飘飘，叶儿落，秋风号……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鸟鸣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呕嘘，呕嘘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才赶鸟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我当什么，原来是寒雀在那里喧叫。当初蔡伯喈进京的时节，此鸟喧叫；如今\n又在那里叫。鸟，鸟，鸟！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清江引顶板） 又听得寒雀鸣于树梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行几步穿过了荒草小道——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才跌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呦呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是何物将老汉绊跌一交？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵唷！我当何物，原来是被偷儿偷去了树木。偷儿，偷儿，为什么单单盗去蔡\n家的树木！令人好恨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我恨偷儿盗树木不学正道，\n偏学浪子无有下梢。\n我急急走，急急跑，急急忙忙到荒郊，特来把松扫。\n只为那当年旧知交，旧知交。"
        },
        {
          "character": "行一步来至在蔡家的墓道、李旺",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "走过了大路走小径，\n逢人便要问几声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀慢着！来到这旷野荒郊，也不知到了陈留郡没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯嘿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉把松扫，老汉把松扫，只为当年旧知交。指望儿子去赶考，荣华富贵爵禄\n高；蔡伯喈，不行孝，忍教二老作饿莩。说什么养儿防备老，数载不归忘劬劳；\n捧着苦李当甜桃，看来愚昧可笑，看来愚昧可笑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "巧啦，那旁有个老丈在那里扫松，不免上前问他一问。\n啊，老伯请啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，请了。小哥施礼为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问你一声，此处可有个陈留郡没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵呵，小哥，你来看，这一带都是陈留郡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的妈呀，今天可找到啦。\n老伯，陈留郡可有一个蔡家府？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们这里，只有蔡家庄，没有蔡家府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不知道，因为蔡家庄有人在京中做官，故而蔡家庄改为蔡家府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人在京中做了官？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是那蔡……嗳，我不敢说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何不说？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们状元爷的官名，岂是胡乱叫得的？被人听见，我吃罪不起呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，小哥，你来看，这旷野荒郊四处无人，就是你我，但讲无妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "讲得的？附耳上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺附耳。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他叫蔡伯喈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺含糊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蔡伯喈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蔡伯喈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀，你是个哑子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是个聋子。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才、李旺同转身。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他叫什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺含糊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蔡伯喈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蔡伯喈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀，你是个哑子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是个聋子。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才、李旺同转身。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他叫什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他叫蔡伯喈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才转身。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张广才 （清江引导板） 你休要提起蔡伯喈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李旺 （清江引摇板） 你大惊小怪为何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问小哥，尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下李旺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你到此作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是来投书的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！原来我的“树”是你偷的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，我投家书。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！你还要偷我的“大树”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么尽打岔！什么偷你的大树，我是下书信的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦……下书信的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错，是下书的。想起来啦，老伯，我和你打听一个人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是哪一个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打听一个张大公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦……张广才。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张大公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张广才。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张大公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张广才。嗳，张大公就是张广才，张广才就是张大公。张广才是他的名字，大\n公是大家称呼他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为什么要问那张大公？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不知道，我们状元老爷，受过张大公的好处，天天思念张大公，吃饭的时候，\n叫一声张大公，喝茶的时候，也叫一声张大公，睡觉的时候，作梦还叫一声\n张大公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀，小哥，你可认得张大公？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不认识他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小老儿便是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！您就是张大公？小人不知，多有得罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺一拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。小哥，你来的不遇时了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么不遇时呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你家老太爷、太夫人下世去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们状元爷给我讲，还有那赵氏五娘呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她身背琵琶，到京城寻找你家老爷去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这么一说，他家里头没有人啦。我要回去交差了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来，难道你空来空去么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老人家，蔡家无人，老的死啦，小的走啦，我这封书信交给城隍，还是交给土\n地呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你讲得有理。也罢，你何不在坟前祭奠祭奠，你回去也好交差，他二老在泉下\n也是含笑的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不认得坟墓在哪儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清江引顶板） 小哥哥，随我来，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就是忘恩负义的蔡伯喈他父母的土坟台；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是五娘亲手葬埋他二老骨骸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦……这就是老太爷、太夫人的坟墓。待我拜上一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "书信何在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在包袱里头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将包袱打开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，将包袱打开。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺打开包袱。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "把书信取出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，把书信取出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺取出书信。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "顶在头上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，顶在头上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺置书于顶上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "跪下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，跪下。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "顺着我的口音说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，老哥哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，老哥哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠲔……"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "𠲔……"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊𠲔……"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊𠲔……"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么也叫他老哥哥哇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不是教我顺着你口音说吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要称太老爷、太夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，要称太老爷、太夫人。再来，再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，老哥，老嫂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太老爷、太夫人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳，“对了”不用啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，“对了”不用。再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，老哥、老嫂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太老爷、太夫人！“对了”不用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呃，不用，不用。老哥、老嫂，你的儿子如今有书信回来，你怎的不言，怎的\n不语啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳！老伯，人死哪有会说话的道理呀？压根儿就没有这么回事儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦……老汉替他二老代讲几句，可使得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这倒使得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，老哥、老嫂，我替你二老教训几句。\n好奴才，好奴才！进京求名，一去数载，并无音信回来；我二老下世，才有书\n信前来，像你这样不肖之子，我恨不能吃尔之肉，喝尔之血！我就打……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才打李旺，跌倒，李旺扶起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我打死你这小奴才！我就打……"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老公公，你打的是我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打错了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我收拾起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李旺卷包裹，拿棍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老公公，您还有什么话说？我要走啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小哥，你当真要走了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当真要走了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然要走了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然要走了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请上受老汉一拜！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才施礼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这不是要折死我吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此拜我又不是拜的你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你拜哪个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我拜的是忘恩负义的——"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清江引二六板）蔡伯喈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听老汉把那蔡家的事儿一一从头说开怀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在家中撇二老竟不归来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他的母终朝每日泪满在胸怀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "最可叹他二老双双冻饿而死就赴了泉台。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卖了些银钱把她公婆来葬埋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是老汉送米又送柴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿她夫妻相会永和谐。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他又把结发的恩情一旦都丢开。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你教那蔡伯喈早早的回家来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小哥！你问他身从哪里得来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就说在这陈留郡荒郊外，有个老者叫张广才，托过小哥把信带。说我一个拜、"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个拜……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才拜，险些跌倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦唷呵……"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你小心点儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张广才 （清江引二六板）教他早早回来，祭扫坟台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我知道。告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双亲死了已无依，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日回来也是迟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夜静水寒鱼不饵，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张广才",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满船空载明月归。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李旺",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张广才、李旺同转身。〖尾声〗。张广才、李旺同下。）"
        }
      ],
